name: Müfit Can Saçinti
summary: Müfit Can Saçinti. Actor: Yasamak Güzel Sey. Müfit Can Saçinti was born on 5 March 1968 in Sungurlu, Corum, Turkey. He is an actor and writer, known for Yasamak Güzel Sey (2017), Maskeler De Düser (2020) and Babamin Ceketi (2018).
